<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Password recovery link - MetCare</title>
    <style>
        #metcare-image {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            text-align: justify;
            text-justify: inter-word;
        }

        .contact-and-img {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            font-family: Arial
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <p id="cabecalho">In a few basic steps you will be able to regain access to your account.</p>

    <p>
        Dear <b>{{name}}</b>,<br></br>
        You received this email because you requested (or someone else) to retrieve the password for your
        account. Please click on the link below, or paste it in your browser to perform the recovery
        of your password, If you have not requested password recovery, please ignore this
        email, and your password will remain intact
    </p>

    <a href="{{link}}"><b>Recover my password</b></a>
    <br />
    <div class="contact-and-img">
        <div>
            <p>
                Met Care | Announcement T +244 923 380 707 |
                <a href="mailto:geral@met-care.com">geral@met-care.com</a>
            </p>
            This is an automatically generated email please do not reply
            <a href="https://www.met-care.com/met-alerta"> met-alerta </a>
        </div>
        <div id="metcare-image">
            <img src="cid:{{cid}}" alt="Met Care" width="800" height="200" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <span style="font-size: 7pt">Before printing this message, think about the environment. This email message,
            as well as any files that may be attached, is reserved for your
            recipients and may contain confidential information or be subject to legal restrictions. If
            is not your recipient or if you received this message due to an error, we ask that you do not
            make any use or dissemination of its content and proceed to the permanent elimination of this
            message and its attachments.
            <br />
        </span>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>